<h1>SL-302 Event Bus & Domain Events</h1>
<p class="small">Prepared for: Morshed | Project: OraBooks Lean MVP | Date: 2026-06-27</p>

<h2>Executive Summary</h2>
<p>SL-302 is implemented and operational for Lean MVP scope. Verification was performed against current code and fresh automated tests.</p>
<div class="box"><strong>Status:</strong> COMPLETE FOR MVP SCOPE</div>

<h2>Implemented Scope</h2>
<ul>
<li>Central Event Bus facade and canonical event module runtime.</li>
<li>Transactional outbox with pending-processing-sent lifecycle.</li>
<li>Retry with backoff and dead-letter handling.</li>
<li>Dead-letter replay, replay-all, and discard operations.</li>
<li>Consumer idempotency tracking via dedicated consumer log table.</li>
<li>Payload validation, event versioning, correlation ID propagation.</li>
<li>Dashboard health visibility and operations hooks.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Primary Files Reviewed</h2>
<ul>
<li>includes/class-orabooks-event-bus.php</li>
<li>includes/events/class-orabooks-event-module.php</li>
<li>tests/OraBooks_EventBus_Test.php</li>
<li>docs/domain-events.md</li>
<li>templates/events/dead-letter-replay.php</li>
</ul>

<h2>Automated Test Result (Fresh)</h2>
<p><strong>Command:</strong> D:\xampp\php\php.exe tests\vendor\phpunit\phpunit\phpunit --configuration tests\phpunit.xml tests\OraBooks_EventBus_Test.php</p>
<ul>
<li>Tests: 12</li>
<li>Assertions: 45</li>
<li>Result: PASS</li>
</ul>

<h2>How to Test Manually</h2>
<ol>
<li>Trigger a domain action that publishes an event and verify outbox row creation.</li>
<li>Run poll-now and verify pending to sent transition.</li>
<li>Simulate consumer failure and verify retry_count increments.</li>
<li>Verify dead_letter state after max retry exhaustion.</li>
<li>Use dead-letter replay and discard operations and verify state changes.</li>
<li>Attempt cross-tenant replay and verify forbidden denial.</li>
<li>Verify event bus health counters in dashboard.</li>
</ol>

<h2>Sign-Off Checklist</h2>
<ul>
<li>SL-302 unit tests pass.</li>
<li>Outbox publish and consumer delivery verified.</li>
<li>Retry and dead-letter flow verified.</li>
<li>Replay/discard operations verified.</li>
<li>Cross-tenant safety verified.</li>
<li>Health dashboard visibility verified.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Conclusion</h2>
<p>SL-302 Event Bus & Domain Events is complete and testable for OraBooks Lean MVP scope.</p>
<p><strong>Recommendation:</strong> Approve SL-302 for MVP sign-off.</p>
